// BP_SodGameMode — Blueprint subclass of ASodGameMode
// Location: /Game/Game/GameModes/BP_SodGameMode

/*
To create in UE5 Editor:
1. Create new Blueprint extending ASodGameMode
2. Set default properties:
   - LightWeaverClass = BP_LightWeaver
   - ShadowWalkerClass = BP_ShadowWalker
   - LightWeaverStartTag = "PlayerStart.Light"
   - ShadowWalkerStartTag = "PlayerStart.Shadow"
   - PlayerControllerClass = BP_SodPlayerController
3. Override Blueprint events:
   - Event OnPlayerJoined → Play spawn sound + show archetype notification
   - Event OnPlayerLeft → Log event
   - Event RestartRound → Reset all puzzle actors
4. Set as GameMode in DefaultEngine.ini:
   GlobalDefaultGameMode=/Game/Game/GameModes/BP_SodGameMode.BP_SodGameMode_C
*/
